features: 4 Plus 6 Large Capacity for Storage: The over door organizer which is 42.52in x 13.78in x 5.5 in (H x L x W), boasts 6 mesh side pockets and 4-tier spacious bins. Each bin has a see-through mesh window for easy accessibility. The spacing between each tier, now increased to 4.33 inches, helps you accommodate different-sized items like wipes, diapers, toilet paper, snacks, gloves, and more daily necessities and baby items. Meantime, side pockets are perfect to hold small items.

Swing-proof & 35.2 LB Load Capacity: Yecaye baby closet organizer stands out for its innovative design and durability. The door organizer hanging features strong stitching to connect the pockets, built-in strengthened side cardboards, strong reinforced bottom cardboards, and fiberglass tubes to prevent sagging and leaning. These features ensure that the baby organizer storage can keep in shape and can hold up to 35.2 lbs with ease.

Odorless & Childproof & Petproof Closet Storage: Crafted from durable and reliable fabric, Yecaye over the door organizer is built to last. No longer do you have to worry about flakey fibers, unpleasant odors, or any other safety hazards that come with typical closet organizers and storage solutions. With Yecaye organization and storage, you can store your items with confidence, knowing that your kids and pets are safe.

Versatile Over the Door Storage: Yecaye bathroom organizer storage makes the most of the vertical space, having extra room freed up for you. Fits children's rooms, storage rooms, offices, bedrooms, bathrooms, pantries, dorms, and other areas where you need to store toys, diapers, baby towels, socks, and other items. With door storage organizer, you can organize your possessions efficiently, making it easier for you to access what you need without wasting time rummaging through piles of clutter.

Easy to Assemble: Afraid of tricky assembly? Don't worry. Our nursery organizers and storage can be assembled in no time at all, simply by hanging the hook on the door, hanging the organizer onto the hooks, and inserting the 4 bottom cardboards. Then, you can start your storage journey. Additionally, our special clip-on hooks add more flexibility, making the back of door storage organizer a universally fit solution for doors less than 1.65" thick.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: We understand that the majority of households have limited storage space at home. Therefore, we specialize in providing home storage products like this 4-tier over the door organizer that features full side stitching to load more but still keep in shape.

What Makes Yecaye Over Door Storage Stand out from the Others Our side cardboard is built-in and sewn together for a beautiful and sturdy look. But other over door storage is need to extra manually insert cardboard, ugly and unattractive.

Our sides of the bathroom organization are reinforced with an interior cardboard and sewn with high-quality fabric, resulting in increased structural integrity and durability while retaining its shape.

We have incorporated fully sealed side seams in our product design, ensuring optimal stability even when carrying heavy loads. With this feature, our bathroom organizer stays upright and secure, without any wobbling or tipping, making it more reliable for your daily use.
